    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >什么是《UNION SURVIVORS》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/72a3debfb50a29c12be3c7b317151e42.poster.avif?t=1758816137\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/72a3debfb50a29c12be3c7b317151e42.webm?t=1758816137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/72a3debfb50a29c12be3c7b317151e42.mp4?t=1758816137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款支持“最多4人在线合作游玩”的Roguelite采矿生存游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挖掘突然大量出现的史莱姆，开辟道路，击退大批敌人吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色的培养方向无限可能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/7b6e02783c132c0d8b01552ebc609e6e.poster.avif?t=1758816137\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/7b6e02783c132c0d8b01552ebc609e6e.webm?t=1758816137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/7b6e02783c132c0d8b01552ebc609e6e.mp4?t=1758816137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人，选择自己喜欢的升级内容来强化自身。<br>等级提升到一定程度后将获得新武器，战斗力也会进一步增强！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据武器和升级的选择不同，构筑方式也会变化，每次挑战都能带来不同的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>采矿并在场地中自由奔跑！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/3c45a9578d77f70f4d45ad33cf134ef4.poster.avif?t=1758816137\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/3c45a9578d77f70f4d45ad33cf134ef4.webm?t=1758816137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3178030/extras/3c45a9578d77f70f4d45ad33cf134ef4.mp4?t=1758816137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挡路的史莱姆中可能藏有玩家强化所需的资源或回复道具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要总是选择安全的道路，有时候也要亲手开辟前路。</p>",
